"After consultation with my Generals and military experts, please be advised that the United States Government will not accept or allow ... Transgender individuals to serve in any capacity in the US Military," Trump wrote on Twitter. However, of those on social media voiced their discontent at Trump, calling him a hypocrite in light of how he has readily backtracked in his support of LGBT people during the US Election period.    Trump's Twitter thread about how transgender people function as a distraction, did not go down well.                      Cape Argus